{
  "texts": [
    "We use the first 50 test samples for evaluation.",
    "tions on the best-performing models using UIs from Section 3.6.",
    "To measure retrievers' performance, we report Recall@1 and Recall@4 which are commonly used in information retrieval (Thakur et al., 2021; Muennighoff et al., 2022).",
    "To measure the final generation performance, we report ROUGE-L (Lin, 2004) and GPT-4 Eval (Zheng et al., 2023a; Liu et al., 2023), which are used in open-domain generation tasks (Zheng et al., 2023a).",
    "For the best models, we additionally perform human evaluation and report the accuracy of the generated answers."
  ]
}